{"tid":1386214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[事後檢討]今朝嘅不合作運動，支持唔支持都請你入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-30T09:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T11:40:03.000Z","uid":129066,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ba517f53bc818196fb85403a044615a684b5f9e2","tid":1386214,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:37:01.000Z","msg":"利申左我今朝係屋企嘆冷氣先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>-----首先我想發洩一下-----</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我認同香港人係時候要停落黎<br />\n面前一個咁嘅社會<br />\n當權者，有實權有武力嘅人唔再守法律，但冇人會被制裁<br />\n黑社會隨街打人，黑警企圖謀殺，攻擊和平嘅人﹑投降嘅人﹑路人等等等<br />\n甚至唔守警例屌柒自己個老細個老老老老.....細細細細個老細<br />\n一個文員去屌公司個GM<br />\n政府﹑執法者 拎住法治 同你講香港係法治社會要守法<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">但當權者不在此限</span>，咁唔係一個法治社會，係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人治</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係權貴就唔洗守法</span><br />\n面對咁嘅暴力社會，示威者真真正正打傷嘅只係，只係一個衝左去示威者入面諗住自己一個打十個行私刑嘅白痴<br />\n其他嘅都係死物<br />\n示威者，<span style=\"color: gold;\">中立嘅</span>記者，<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔關事嘅</span>路人，<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">傷左幾多個呀？</span></strong><br />\n如果香港輸左，等同<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">法治﹑制度同時崩壞</span></strong></span><br />\n冇人會再係到做長期投資，冇人會拎一個咁<span style=\"color: orange;\">唔穩定</span>嘅香港做投資核心<br />\n無錯呀你呢<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">幾日仲有工翻，但一年﹑兩年之後呢？</span></strong>你嘅下一代呢？<br />\n我真係冇辦法係一個咁唔穩定冇法治冇人權，違反曬我同你都認同嘅基本普世價值嘅地方--香港，去生兒育女？咁嘅環境，我唔識教<br />\n你仲同我講你中立，一個事不關己己不關心嘅樣？<br />\n仲繼續如常生活？<br />\n當然你有成頭家等你開飯，唔翻工會死就算啦<br />\n有錢出錢有力，盡做啦</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">--------------發洩完---------------</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n但係但係<br />\n根據屋企人﹑電視、電台嘅回應係<br />\n有好多人覺得係後生搞事，阻住佢地翻工<br />\n<br />\n呢個抗爭<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">一旦比人標籤</span></strong>左做<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>年輕人</span>嘅示威</strong><br />\n我地就輸架啦<br />\n<br />\n其他人無論支持﹑反對﹑中立(屌)<br />\n都只會係一個唔關我事嘅樣<br />\n就算<span style=\"color: orange;\">立場上支持都好，佢地唔會行出黎</span><br />\n<br />\n對於今日閙後生搞事嘅人<br />\n第一<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">佢地仲未醒</span></strong><br />\n而我相信今日仲未醒嘅人，係因為佢地唔識接收資訊<br />\n唔會亦都唔知有咩方法去了解社會嘅真相<br />\n第二<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">佢地根本唔知今日有不合作活動</span></strong><br />\n打亂左佢地嘅計劃<br />\n突如其來唔如意嘅事，往往會令人鼓躁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，我地要做嘅係，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>加強文宣</strong></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n比<strong>得單一資料渠道嘅人</strong>了解真相，<span style=\"color: gold;\">一日仲有人反對<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&ldquo;暴力&ldquo;</span>示威，即係仲有人可以拉攏</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">主動</span></strong>比資訊支持但唔識收集資訊嘅人，唔好teamkill影響到佢地嘅plan<br />\n如果佢地真係有要翻工/出去嘅原因，可以提早作安排<br />\n<br />\n暫時我諗到嘅方法都係得<span style=\"color: orange;\">街站同傳單</span><br />\n一個一個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>懶人包日程包</strong></span>咁派出去<br />\n簡單直接，就算<span style=\"color: red;\">幾忙幾懶</span>都可以知道發生咩事<br />\n<br />\nfor打工仔：<br />\n朝早翻工時間派傳單<br />\n放工時間擺街站<br />\n<br />\nfor師奶呀叔呀伯：<br />\n朝早公園傾計？<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">噓寒問暖</span>佢地應該buy</span><br />\n中午街市街站？<br />\n<br />\nfor身邊既後生：<br />\n你自己搞掂佢啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">外國文宣我地就做得多啦</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">係時候拉攏翻<strong>香港人</strong>支持</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">自己香港自己救！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">利申我好得閒<br />\n有冇人已經做緊呢呢野可以add我入gp</span>"},{"pid":"26aa65b0810ea4f6fa1db49cb622a7bc4ef91816","tid":1386214,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:37:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"77cc61424e8a6b13b135bbee52fbf523258de171","tid":1386214,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:37:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20a5ad1ff3163487a3bc49184a60079b23a7acf1","tid":1386214,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:37:43.000Z","msg":"pushpushpush"},{"pid":"481f0684d4a306e9475dae7b927da3fa47208652","tid":1386214,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:37:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8fcf981be91a081e90df19f2436ce691d34f7b0e","tid":1386214,"uid":67645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:37:56.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n野貓式堵路 打遊擊先係出路！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386051</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"16d2370d95f1e0029fd30a8d7ba38f2556e22ee3","tid":1386214,"uid":259613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:38:20.000Z","msg":"[香城online]前線一個好嚴重既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1386126/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1386126/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"fd82783f861b071e49f05f9d18387b934fa1a37f","tid":1386214,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:38:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4eec391fe732042a374eeadf5c658da5b8478325","tid":1386214,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:38:33.000Z","msg":"所以我話星期六日搞都得"},{"pid":"bcad1310cc2108f0b14d873061cf975d9b66dad9","tid":1386214,"uid":259515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:39:03.000Z","msg":"airdrop schedule + lennon wall + flyers (can put into apartment mailbox)"},{"pid":"50481fdb04e629e486d4128e5db1e6bb40706bfb","tid":1386214,"uid":1581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:39:42.000Z","msg":"Pish 營養post"},{"pid":"418ee481f03ceadb03e158d0e452ad50db76fd42","tid":1386214,"uid":69933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:40:19.000Z","msg":"好似之前咁預先有公開信？"},{"pid":"8517892a9539af1ebf2e2a0cc74b630b32134812","tid":1386214,"uid":26130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:41:58.000Z","msg":"相關閱讀<br />\n<br />\n[不合作運動]其實我哋未取得最大嘅成效<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1385956/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1385956/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c652ef8ed23477b4885cc4cb7302b16c6a4768a2","tid":1386214,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"418ee481f03ceadb03e158d0e452ad50db76fd42","tid":1386214,"uid":69933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:40:19.000Z","msg":"好似之前咁預先有公開信？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:44:32.000Z","msg":"每逢有機會影響到人的活動都要有<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">大力</span>宣傳</strong><br />\n要<span style=\"color: orange;\">大力</span>到連只有電視電台做接收渠道的人都知道<br />\n<br />\n最好有個穩定的渠道<br />\n<br />\n可以用兩老/兩老朋友做測試"},{"pid":"ae1470ccd7a562e53dcf64c378149d998c7a92de","tid":1386214,"uid":174289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfdf2fe173931bfbed78d9d4fbf9d1ecbe691b9","tid":1386214,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae1470ccd7a562e53dcf64c378149d998c7a92de","tid":1386214,"uid":174289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:50:17.000Z","msg":"airdrop個年齡層始終唔夠廣，仲要得apple收到<br />\n如果airdrop配不嫌其煩forward去whatsapp gp/同朋友講成效會更大"},{"pid":"36f31d121f0b9a1048e5292b738a810766529c95","tid":1386214,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:50:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ca8cc09b8ea23f414782536ddc6b4c27fe98c293","tid":1386214,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:51:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"960fa661c53eb17412f2eaad571cf5cae4886f5a","tid":1386214,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ddadc57771c02630d3e90f1e3a494c1fdc90fc","tid":1386214,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:51:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3fce3a6da3c692f193f9019ffb74833c0cc5aa53","tid":1386214,"uid":69933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:53:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef7255a18917700c6b348c99fa32a227316b076c","tid":1386214,"uid":234343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:53:31.000Z","msg":"阻大家小小時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱開咗個twitter宣傳85活動 希望全世界都知咩事 最重要係想通知外國記者85全港大罷工 希望受到關注 如果你地有twitter account都可以幫手retweet一下 一傳十 十傳百 記得send埋俾身邊有twitter嘅親朋戚友 感謝大家為香港岀一分力<br />\n<br />\n時代革命 光復香港<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/savehk2019/status/1155755002649989120?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsavehk2019%2Fstatus%2F1155755002649989120%3Fs%3D21&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCuXGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=373f3bac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsavehk2019%2Fstatus%2F1155755002649989120%3Fs%3D21&h=ce270015\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/savehk2019/status/1155755002649989120?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"a70aa4d4938d9b2a98b9e82a04ea80e677c69c39","tid":1386214,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:54:51.000Z","msg":"再塞地鐵<br />\n一定要預早幾日預告定！<br />\n佢地有心理準備，有重要事可以預早規劃<br />\n預早幾日講，做足宣傳先去塞！"},{"pid":"28ff88e9041c6025135e759fb3ce98b4866b4ea6","tid":1386214,"uid":272592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba517f53bc818196fb85403a044615a684b5f9e2","tid":1386214,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T09:37:01.000Z","msg":"利申左我今朝係屋企嘆冷氣先<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>-----首先我想發洩一下-----</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我認同香港人係時候要停落黎<br />\n面前一個咁嘅社會<br />\n當